| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4701 — Recovery Inhibition (cephalus)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 399dff59-9d67-5aa5-ba74-3f9a9c8bfac3"
